title: Bug 116564 - The title of hyperlink builder changes with settings
EB: Bug 116564 - The title of hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', now it changes with settings.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'.
2. Click on 'OK' to save and close the hyperlink builder.
3. Reopen the hyperlink builder.
